These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
City: new-york, colone, venice, rome
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, may, november
1. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in may##2
6. the person traveling to rome is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| City   | rome | new-york     | venice | colone |
| Birthday     | june     | may | november  | february      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, december, april, september
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, emerald, lavender, aquamarine
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes white is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Birthday   | november | december    | september     | april  |
| Color     | white    | lavender | emerald | aquamarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, ebony, light-blue, apricot
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, turkish, british, french
1. the french is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
2. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
3. the british is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the italian is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
5. the british is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Color   | ebony   | light-blue   | black  | apricot |
| Nationality           | turkish | french | british | italian  |

