.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different games are played: chess, poker, mah-jongg, billiard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, blues, electronic
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing billiard is between the person playing chess and the fan of blues##2
3. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
4. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Game         | poker | chess | billiard | mah-jongg  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | rock   | electronic  | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, davidoff, havana, prince
There 4 different types of food: orange, banana, eggplant, pomegranate
1. the person eating banana is on the far left##1
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Cigar   | baccarat    | davidoff   | havana | prince    |
| Food      | banana | orange | eggplant       | pomegranate |

