.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, begonia, bellflower, daffodil
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, police-officer, project-manager, accountant
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the project-manager is between the accountant and the person who growsbellflower##2
3. the teacher is between the project-manager and the person who growsiris##2
4. the accountant is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Flower    | iris | bellflower | daffodil | begonia |
| Job   | police-officer | teacher  | project-manager    | accountant  |

