.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, disco, folk
City: edinburgh, new-york, liverpool, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the fan of disco is between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of folk##2
5. the person traveling to new-york is the person traveling to new-york##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to liverpool and the fan of folk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | folk | disco | hip-hop     |
| City     | edinburgh | boston  | new-york   | liverpool |

