.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, ivory, red, lavender
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf, basketball, cricket
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes lavender is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Color         | lavender | red | yellow | ivory   |
| Sport   | golf | basketball | skateboarding      | cricket |

