.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, family, zombie, spy
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, video-games, baking, collecting
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching family movies is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre     | superhero | family   | zombie      | spy      |
| Hobby   | video-games     | baking | photography | collecting |

