.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, snake, hamster, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, jet-ski, airplane
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the owner of the hamster is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the quad-bike##2
3. the owner of the snake is the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Pet   | cat | snake | hamster      | goat   |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | quad-bike    | trike | airplane |

