.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, chestnut, green, blue
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, fanta, 7up
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
6. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Color       | blood-red | green | blue    | chestnut      |
| Beverage   | fanta       | 7up       | milk | water |

