.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bluemaster, pall-mall, ritmeester
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, water, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Cigar   | dunhill     | bluemaster  | ritmeester | pall-mall |
| Beverage     | lemonade | hot-chocolate | cola     | water    |

