.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, may, september
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, pilot, lawyer, architect
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the pilot is on the left or right of the bartender##3
4. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
6. the pilot is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
7. the bartender is on the right of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | january | may  | september | october |
| Job           | lawyer     | architect | bartender    | pilot     |

