.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, gothic-revival, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, cycling, volleyball
1. the palace house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| House   | farmhouse  | cape-cod | palace  | gothic-revival      |
| Sport    | volleyball | cricket | cycling | skiing |

