4. the wooden house is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the colonial house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
6. the colonial house is the person who's sport is skiing##1
7. the wooden house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Sport         | cricket | rugby | weightlifting | skiing |
| House   | craftsman     | townhouse       | wooden   | colonial      |

