2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the canadian##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the indian##3
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Hobby   | dancing | collecting  | reading  | cooking |
| Nationality           | indian    | canadian | colombian | mexican |

