.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, cauliflower, plum, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, polish, canadian
1. the polish is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is the canadian##1
3. the person eating artichoke is on the left or right of the canadian##3
4. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the canadian is on the left or right of the polish##3
6. the colombian is on the left of the person eating lime##1
7. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Food   | cauliflower     | lime     | plum          | artichoke |
| Nationality      | colombian | japanese | canadian | polish  |

 